â€¢â€¢â€¢Example of a Hint:
<main>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <form>
      <div>
        <label for="url">URL</label>
        <input type="text" id="url" name="url" aria-describedby="name-hint">
        <span id="name-hint" class="hint">For example, https://example.com</span>
      </div>
      <button>Save</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</main>


â€¢â€¢CSS Value:
button {
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

.hint {
  display: block;
  padding-top: 0.4em;
}

label {
  font-size: 1.5em;
}
